  <summary date="2019-04-18T20:55:21Z" status="Introduced in House">Preventing Rogue and Foreign Actors From Evading Sanctions Act 

This bill directs the Department of the Treasury to report on the use of new financial technologies (e.g., digital currencies) in terrorism and other illicit activities and develop a strategy to mitigate this use.</summary>
